sm\"><div class=\"font-bold\">ZiQia.cc</div><div class=\"text-[13px] text-on-surface-variant\">2026年07月13日<!-- --> · <!-- -->3 分钟阅读</div></div><a class=\"ml-auto rounded-full bg-google-blue-cta px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(60,64,67,0.3)] transition-colors hover:bg-[#1765CC]\" href=\"/cn/posts/why-tech-docs-fail/\">阅读全文</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><div class=\"mb-7 flex items-end justify-between border-b border-outline-variant pb-4\"><div><h2 class=\"font-heading text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">最新文章</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant\">AI 开发的实践、思考与工具</p></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"group overflow-hidden rounded-card border border-outline-variant bg-surface transition-shadow hover:shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(60,64,67,0.15),0_4px_12px_rgba(60,64,67,0.1)]\"><a class=\"block\" href=\"/cn/posts/du-wan-wen-dang-bu-hui-yong/\"><div class=\"h-36 w-full\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, #E6F4EA 0%, #34A853 60%, #34A853 100%)\"><span class=\"m-3 inline-block rounded-full bg-white/95 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold backdrop-blur\" style=\"color:#34A853\">AI 编码工作流</span></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-bold leading-snug\">读完技术文档还是不会用？——从「能力清单」到「意图地图」的鸿沟</h3><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">官方文档按&quot;有什么&quot;组织，但你的问题永远是&quot;怎么做&quot;——这种结构性错配注定无法靠&quot;通读&quot;来解决。</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[13px] text-on-surface-variant\"><span>2026年07月13日<!-- --> · <!-- -->3 分钟阅读</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-google-blue-cta\">阅读全文<!-- --> →</span></div></div></a></article><article class=\"group overflow-hidden rounded-card border border-outline-variant bg-surface transition-shadow hover:shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(60,64,67,0.15),0_4px_12px_rgba(60,64,67,0.1)]\"><a class=\"block\" href=\"/cn/posts/ai-coding-cli-tools-comparison/\"><div class=\"h-36 w-full\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, #FCE8E6 0%, #EA4335 60%, #EA4335 100%)\"><span class=\"m-3 inline-block rounded-full bg-white/95 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold backdrop-blur\" style=\"color:#EA4335\">工具生态</span></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-bold leading-snug\">五大 AI 编程 CLI 工具横评：OpenCode、Claude Code、Codex CLI 怎么选？</h3><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">横向对比五大 AI 编程命令行工具的核心能力、优劣势与适用场景，帮你做出最适合自己的选择。</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[13px] text-on-surface-variant\"><span>2026年07月13日<!-- --> · <!-- -->5 分钟阅读</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-google-blue-cta\">阅读全文<!-- --> →</span></div></div></a></article><article class=\"group overflow-hidden rounded-card border border-outline-variant bg-surface transition-shadow hover:shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(60,64,67,0.15),0_4px_12px_rgba(60,64,67,0.1)]\"><a class=\"block\" href=\"/cn/posts/rust-memory/\"><div class=\"h-36 w-full\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, #FCE8E6 0%, #EA4335 60%, #EA4335 100%)\"><span class=\"m-3 inline-block rounded-full bg-white/95 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold backdrop-blur\" style=\"color:#EA4335\">工具生态</span></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-bold leading-snug\">Rust 内存模型浅析</h3><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">理解所有权、借用与生命周期，写出更安全的系统级代码。</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[13px] text-on-surface-variant\"><span>2024年11月01日<!-- --> · <!-- -->1 分钟阅读</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-google-blue-cta\">阅读全文<!-- --> →</span></div></div></a></article><article class=\"group overflow-hidden rounded-card border border-outline-variant bg-surface transition-shadow hover:shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(60,64,67,0.15),0_4px_12px_rgba(60,64,67,0.1)]\"><a class=\"block\" href=\"/cn/posts/message-queue/\"><div class=\"h-36 w-full\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, #E6F4EA 0%, #34A853 60%, #34A853 100%)\"><span class=\"m-3 inline-block rounde